    <title>SAG-AFTRA calls for a strike against League of Legends </title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="Key art from League of Legends featuring two women, Vi and Jinx, standing back to back with their signature weapons" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nsL5CBzSz1bJggBJ6GlEq5Pt4Ok=/2x0:1919x1278/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73607840/Wild_Rift_Key_Art__Riot_Regions_.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Image: Riot Games&lt;/figcaption&gt;
